{"id":"265854217_Relaxed_Hensel_lifting_of_triangular_sets","abstract":"In this paper, we present a new lifting algorithm for triangular sets over general p-adic rings. Our contribution is to give, for any p-adic triangular set, a shifted algorithm of which the triangular set is a fixed point. Then we can apply the relaxed recursive p-adic framework and deduce a relaxed lifting algorithm for this triangular set.\nWe compare our algorithm to the existing technique and report on implementations inside the C++ library Geomsolvex of Mathemagixvan der Hoeven et al. (2002). Our new relaxed algorithm is competitive and compare favorably on some examples.","authors":["Romain Lebreton"],"meta":["January 2014Journal of Symbolic Computation 68","DOI:10.1016/j.jsc.2014.09.012"],"references":["269033692_Fast_arithmetic_for_triangular_sets_From_theory_to_practice","266659160_Faster_relaxed_multiplication","265519861_Solving_Zero-Dimensional_Systems_Through_the_Rational_Univariate_Representation","233512878_Relax_but_Dont_be_Too_Lazy","228917565_On_the_complexity_of_the_D5_principle","224959310_Power_Series_Solutions_of_Singular_q-Differential_Equations","222830657_New_algorithms_for_relaxed_multiplication","222531269_Newton's_method_and_FFT_trading","221564637_Lifting_techniques_for_triangular_decompositions","221564033_A_Fixed_Point_Method_for_Power_Series_Computation","221420468_Algebraic_Solution_of_Systems_of_Polynomial_Equations_Using_Groebner_Bases","220160974_Homotopy_techniques_for_multiplication_modulo_triangular_sets","324407379_Differential_Algebra","285838677_Spin_glass_problem_by_the_method_of_integral_equation_of_the_effective_field","285022936_Basic_principles_of_mechanical_theorem_proving_in_elementary_geometries","281357477_Contributions_to_relaxed_algorithms_and_polynomial_system_solving","278717310_Algorithmes_-_disons_rapides_-_pour_la_decomposition_d'une_variete_algebrique_en_composantes_irreductibles_et_equidimensionnelles","265675598_Algorithmes_-_disons_ra